Threshold.name: ICReads
Threshold.explanation: Number of Internal Control (IC) reads within a sample (Minimum threshold = 1,000)

Threshold.name: IC_Median
Threshold.explanation: Sample IC reads relative to the median (Within +/- 40% of the plate median)

Threshold.name: NumReads
Threshold.explanation: Number of reads within a sample (Minimum threshold = 500,000)

Threshold.name: Detectability
Threshold.explanation: Percentage of targets that are detectable (target is considered detectable if > 50% of samples are above LOD) (Minimum threshold = 90%)

Threshold.name: Failed_IPC
Threshold.explanation: Number of CAL samples with Sample QC warnings (Maximum threshold = 0)

Threshold.name: Failed_SC
Threshold.explanation: Number of AQSC samples with Sample QC warnings (Maximum threshold = 0)

Threshold.name: Failed_Targets
Threshold.explanation: Percentage of Targets with Target QC warnings (Maximum threshold = 10%)

Threshold.name: ICRead_CV
Threshold.explanation: Coefficient of variation of internal control Parseable Matching reads across all wells (Maximum threshold = 25%)

Threshold.name: IPCRead_CV
Threshold.explanation: Coefficient of variation of Parseable Matching reads across all CALs (Maximum threshold = 25%)

Threshold.name: IPCTarget_CV
Threshold.explanation: Median coefficient of variation of all CAL targets (Maximum threshold = 10%)

Threshold.name: MinReads
Threshold.explanation: Minimum number of Parseable Matching reads for the run (Minimum threshold = 100,000,000)

Threshold.name: SCRead_CV
Threshold.explanation: Coefficient of variation of Parseable Matching reads across all AQSCs (Maximum threshold = 25%)

Threshold.name: SCTarget_CV
Threshold.explanation: Median of coefficient of variation of normalized reads of all AQSC targets (Maximum threshold = 10%)

Threshold.name: Target_Conc_Accuracy
Threshold.explanation: Experimental vs Theoretical average AQSC concentration accuracy (Within +/-30% of theoretical, calculated on AQ targets)

Threshold.name: Target_Conc_CV
Threshold.explanation: Target-specific AQSC coefficient of variation (Maximum threshold = 30%, calculated on AQ targets)

Threshold.name: Target_Conc_CV_RQ
Threshold.explanation: Target-specific AQSC (normalized reads) coefficient of variation (Maximum threshold = 30%)

Threshold.name: Target_Detectability
Threshold.explanation: Target Detectability (Minimum threshold = 50)

Threshold.name: Target_IPC_Min_Reads
Threshold.explanation: Minimum number of reads for the median of an IPC target (Minimum threshold = 200)

Threshold.name: Target_Min_Reads
Threshold.explanation: Percentage of targets who's samples meet the threshold of at least 200 reads (Minimum threshold = 90%)
